summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical overhead and underground distribution easements over portions of Tract 26, Moore's Five Acre Tracts; portion of northeast quarter of the northeast quarter of Section 11, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; portion of Vacated alley in Block 14, Byron Addition; portion of Parcels A and B, City of Seattle Short Subdivision No. 8802924; Beginning at the intersection of the south line of south 113th Street with the east line of the West 20 feet of Tract 19 of Saulsberry Beach.
